.LP
Broadcasts the message \fIMsg\fR\& asynchronously to the registered process \fIName\fR\& on the specified nodes\&.
.RE
.LP
.nf

.B
sbcast(Name, Msg) -> {GoodNodes, BadNodes}
.br
.fi
.br
.RS
.LP
Types:

.RS 3
Name = atom()
.br
Msg = term()
.br
GoodNodes = BadNodes = [node()]
.br
.RE
